---
// src/pages/apply.astro
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="APPLY" activeKey="apply">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 space-y-12">
    
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-slate-950 shadow-md border border-slate-900 text-center py-12 px-6 md:p-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <img src="/apply.jpg" alt="能登の良い未来背景" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center opacity-30">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950/90 via-blue-950/80 to-slate-900/70"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black text-white leading-tight drop-shadow-md">
          能登の良い未来を<br class="sm:hidden">あなたの個性を活かして<br>一緒に作りませんか？
        </h2>
        <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-orange-400 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        <p class="text-slate-200 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto font-medium opacity-95">
          NSF PROJECTsでは、日本全国から集まる仲間と共に活動を推進する学生メンバーを随時募集しています。あなたの個性を活かせる場所がきっとあります。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center space-y-4 pt-4">
      <a href="https://discord.gg/cJBNpdXxKD" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 font-black text-white transition-all duration-200 bg-blue-600 rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl active:scale-95">
        <span class="mr-3">Discordに参加してメンバーになる</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
      </a>
      <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Join our online community on Discord</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xs text-center space-y-3">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-slate-950 text-sm">全国に広がる仲間</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">北海道から沖縄まで、全国の中高生・学生メンバーが多数集まっています。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xs text-center space-y-3">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-slate-950 text-sm">個性を活かす</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">「こんな支援をしたい！」という思いから、誰でも新しいプロジェクトを立ち上げられます。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xs text-center space-y-3">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-slate-950 text-sm">Discordで連携</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">オンラインツールを活用し、地域を問わず活発なコミュニケーションを行っています。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xs flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-6 max-w-lg">
        <img src="/IMG_1413.jpg" alt="えぬくま" class="w-20 h-20 object-contain">
        <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
          <h4 class="font-black text-blue-600 text-sm mb-1 tracking-wider uppercase">Official Mascot</h4>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-[11px] leading-relaxed">
            公式マスコットの「えぬくま」君です。君の参加を、全メンバーと一緒に楽しみに待ってるよ！
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
